tions"><ul class="item-actions"><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="8873484"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">1 条评论</span></button></li><li class="bull">&bull;</li><li><a href="/question/41665273">38 个回答</a></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Question"><link itemprop="url" href="/question/271413096"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="22588964"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="271413096"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="link" target="_blank" href="/question/271413096">有种传言说疫苗只打国家免费的，不要打付费的，是不是有一定道理？</a></h2></div><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="22588964"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">1 条评论</span></button></li><li class="bull">&bull;</li><li><a href="/question/271413096">4 个回答</a></li></ul></div></li></ul></div></div></section><aside class="page-sidebar pure-u-1 pure-u-md-7-24"><div class="unit-inner"><div class="shameimaru-placeholder" data-loc="roundtable_up" data-params='{"roundtable_token": "yimiaojiezhong"}'></div><div class="module organizations"><div class="module-header"><h3>主办方</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1003bb2fb402f1b21f60b7d5ca555b71_l.jpg" alt="知乎圆桌" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'>知乎圆桌</a><div class="bio">举办过 255 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">知乎发起的在线嘉宾讨论，详情请点击：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/20139321" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$20139321'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c5de9ad4ede00765165f3c6c6daaa359_l.jpg" alt="健康中国" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/20139321" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$20139321'>健康中国</a><div class="bio">举办过 3 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description"><p>「<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/org/jian-kang-zhong-guo/activities" data-editable="true" data-title="(1 条消息)健康中国 - 知乎" class="">健康中国</a>」是国家卫生健康委员会顺应互联网传播趋势，建立的可视化、亲民化、IP化的新媒体矩阵。采取多帐号、多平台联合的形式，实现与广大群众的直接沟通，成为国家卫生健康委员会传递医疗行业资讯、传播健康知识的新平台。</p></p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/jiang-ren-jie-63-55" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$jiang-ren-jie-63-55'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a6da33e6f8d170bc8cce62760c68f0cf_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="姜仁杰"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/yimiaojiezhong/jiang-ren-jie-63-55/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/jiang-ren-jie-63-55" data-hovercard='p$t$jiang-ren-jie-63-55'>姜仁杰</a><div class="bio">主任医师</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/li-jing-64-36-69" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$li-jing-64-36-69'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b7f2bb2c9b8ba747f3b8a2576cb365a5_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="李静"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/yimiaojiezhong/li-jing-64-36-69/